{"tid":1917144,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林卓廷批馮驊反口准長者打尖投票 周浩鼎否認有偏幫：係佢哋身體情況嘅問題","createTime":"2020-03-09T10:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T00:57:56.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ceae79e30cbce26cdb26cb5c54d9addc00079509","tid":1917144,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:14:42.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）選管會今就立法會選舉指引提出修訂，讓所有年滿70歲之長者優先投票，被質疑傾斜親建制人士。民主黨立法會議員林卓廷批選管會主席馮驊「反口」：「全世界都係咁投架啦」；民建聯立法會議員周浩鼎則表示歡迎修訂，否認政府「偏幫」建制派：「社會上好多政策都對長者有優待，係佢哋身體情況嘅問題」。<br />\n<br />\n記者：湯璧瑜<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1071419\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1071419&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=e2677ed6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1071419&h=939d06bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1071419</a>"},{"pid":"626c80fadf1765fac440841d08b784a298f33d00","tid":1917144,"uid":103230,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:15:55.000Z","msg":"長者身體一定有問題？<br />\n你就有問題呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce713b36a54aa2e5f70384d1a86d57b63dd7308a","tid":1917144,"uid":103405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f736153b1c2f9a474c6a615b3d80673d658a45dd","tid":1917144,"uid":225798,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:18:09.000Z","msg":"思想有問題就唔應該投票"},{"pid":"acf945d95df287529c3fb129dd13aa2e85281137","tid":1917144,"uid":22959,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:18:43.000Z","msg":"周浩鼎即係歧視傷殘人士啫"},{"pid